\exsrc VAL120
\ex Bago Malesia haŋma konno.
\exe This one must be sent to Malaysia.
\exsrc VAL150
\ex Cuwa tima kina lokmeiʔma konno.
\exe One has to fill in water and boil it.
\exsrc VAL176
\com the embedded clause normally behaves like S of the embedded verb; embedded P/T/G linked to O-AGR may raise to matrix S-AGR
\qst

