\lex nuwagi
\alt nuwaŋgi
\alt nawaŋgi
\alt nuwāgi
\ps n
\de a.ritual
\seme one of the most important annual worships in Chintang, taking place around September. It is centered around the offering of the first rice harvest to ancestral deities and is very similar to the complementary Yupuŋ worship
